name: Holistic Healing By Design
tag_list: addictions, weight-loss, anxiety, stress, therapy, therapy-nyc
overview:
Based in New York City Holistic Healing By Design offers one-on-one counseling and hypnosis sessions and utilizes NLP (Neuro-Linguistic Programming) in the treatment of addictions and phobias, weight loss programmes, promoting wellbeing as well as stress and anxiety relief.

Whether your goal is to break unhealthy habits or enrich your personal or professional life, hypnosis & NLP can help you to lose weight, get relief from stress and anxiety, get rid of addictions, be free from phobias, manage your time effectively, and build stronger, more meaningful relationships.
